{"tid":2259980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"軍方高層誓保政治中立","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T08:31:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2dddb3dbc1064cac8616b1fa2dbce30697343fce","tid":2259980,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/M4DTL4HFIJFXNDDU3S63DLYJ4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FM4DTL4HFIJFXNDDU3S63DLYJ4M%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0cdbdf5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201027%2FM4DTL4HFIJFXNDDU3S63DLYJ4M%2F&h=27bd552c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201027/M4DTL4HFIJFXNDDU3S63DLYJ4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n軍方高層誓保政治中立<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nEv4mSz_N03LFO9nE9bbkkKHg6U=/1092x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WIJALXKWBRAZBAWNZD5XFPMWJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnEv4mSz_N03LFO9nE9bbkkKHg6U%3D%2F1092x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWIJALXKWBRAZBAWNZD5XFPMWJY.jpg&h=c47f4f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■米萊堅持軍方保持政治中立。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國總統選舉一旦有候選人拒絕承認結果後，外界關注如投票、點票以至選後活動出現大混亂，軍方可否介入平亂。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：布殊 戈爾為選票對簿公堂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n票站部署不可行<br />\n<br />\n美國憲法列明，軍方只可在極端情況下介入，一般情況下，軍方在選舉中沒有任何角色，維持秩序由警方負責。不過《暴亂法》（Insurrection Act）理論上容許現役軍人扮演類似警察的角色，而州長有權在緊急情況下可出動隸屬軍方的國民警衞隊，以應對天災，或在暴動現場協助警方執法。州長和軍方領袖曾討論在票站或選後活動現場如出現混亂，會否出動軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n自總統特朗普暗示或不接受選舉結果後，。。。。。。。。。而法例列明，總統確有權在聯邦層面調動國民警衞隊應對國內緊急情況。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：郵遞投票問題勢起訴訟<br />\n<br />\n《暴亂法》指總統有權在特定情況下，。。。。。。。。。。。，不過州長在法律上可否阻止總統運用該法例就成疑。<br />\n<br />\n在票站部署軍人，。。。。。。。。。不過過往未曾有軍方領袖在總統使用《暴亂法》時拒絕遵從指令。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"}]}